OSSEC Wazuh Ruleset - Installer and Updater


The script requires Python version 2.7 or superior and asume that OSSEC is installed at the default path (/var/ossec).

Pretty simple usage:

Choose what do you want to install/update:

-r, Rules and Decoders
-c, Rootchecks
-a, Both of them


Choose update or installation:

-u, update
no arguments, installation


Usage examples.

Full installation:
./ossec_ruleset.py -a

Full update:
./ossec_ruleset.py -a -u



Check how to schedule weekly automatic updates at the full documentation: http://documentation.wazuh.com/en/latest/ossec_rule_set.html
